commit.message:
_dispatch returns @body

This means you can do simple tests of your controller using
  @controller = MyController.new(@fake_request)
  @body = @controller._dispatch(index)

Add Exec{ logoutput=> on_failure }

This option only writes the output of the command to the log if the command
failed.

Allow alternative values for the 'new' and 'edit' actions in resourceful routes.

map.resource :schools, :as => 'escuelas', :path_names => { :new => 'nueva' }

Closes #11181.  [ivanvr]
